{"tid":185352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【拜山要小心】清明掃墓燒紙錢　杭州多人中鉛毒 (18:01)","createTime":"2017-04-03T11:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T16:54:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"735b3572b58bca0151f9e27e66dbc7914aadf8fb","tid":185352,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:48:45.000Z","msg":"2017/4/3<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明天是清明節，不少人掃墓時會燒紙錢、紙紮品等拜祭先人。在杭州，近日有多人因接觸冥幣、元寶等祭品而中鉛毒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n杭州市紅十字會醫院職業病科主任醫生李國輝表示，今年醫院接收多名與冥幣、銀元寶有過接觸史的患者，全都因吸入有毒物質中鉛毒，當中有人是冥幣加工廠工人，有清理焚燒後祭品垃圾的工人，亦有掃墓的普通百姓。<br />\n<br />\n其他報道：內地網店「代人掃墓」服務應市　即場視像通話供客人與先人對話　100人仔有交易<br />\n<br />\n李表示內地很多廠商生產的錫箔紙錢，實際上是用鉛箔替代，燃燒後會產生大量的氧化鉛危害人體；不少加上各種彩色圖案的冥幣及紙紮品，所用的顏料中亦含有大量鉛，焚燒時有毒的微粒會隨氣流在空氣飄浮，人們吸入呼吸說會影響健康，嚴重會導致鉛中毒。<br />\n<br />\n根據本港衛生防護中心資料，人體意外地接觸高濃度的鉛量，可導致急性中鉛毒，病徵包括腹痛及嘔吐；慢性中鉛毒的影響包括神經系統發展影響、貧血、高血壓、消化系統病徵、腎功能受損、神經系統受損、生育能力受損和不良懷孕結果，嬰幼兒、孕婦及餵哺母乳的婦女較易受鉛影響。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170403/s00004/1491211193632#sthash.qzLvXhhW.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170403%2Fs00004%2F1491211193632%23sthash.qzLvXhhW.dpuf&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6DwikzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=9b015dbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170403%2Fs00004%2F1491211193632%23sthash.qzLvXhhW.dpuf&h=e13fb8dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170403/s00004/1491211193632#sthash.qzLvXhhW.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"6f83a20022992d44a9cbef9246c01d7f2a1df080","tid":185352,"uid":10319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:49:36.000Z","msg":"下年變被人拜果個"},{"pid":"92a6a9e077784838a7f63680fd145a873e3f7ef8","tid":185352,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:50:58.000Z","msg":"不嬲唔buy燒衣紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26785a829b49b4dddeed2b5d0c5afc7d47a5c7f3","tid":185352,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T12:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3618c46464ff7ea2db81a29252450939efdfa41c","tid":185352,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T12:35:13.000Z","msg":"幾好呀，燒紙錢都係想表達對親人嘅心意啫，而家直接落去見佢咪幾好"},{"pid":"bc8b3567a094575713b801b0c58025b079c5ce54","tid":185352,"uid":56714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T12:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾好呀，燒紙錢都係想表達對親人嘅心意啫，而家直接落去見佢咪幾好</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d2442424c7e43a4c71d2d8610a24b292627dd9","tid":185352,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}